edu.ncsu.csc216.pack_scheduler.course

Class Activity

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ncsu.csc216.pack_scheduler.course.Activity
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Conflict
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Course

    public abstract class Activity
extends java.lang.Object
implements Conflict
    Abstract class that represents a scheduled activity. An Activity Object has a title, the meeting days that it occurs, and the start/end time.
    Author:
    Dominic Brown (dtbrown5)
